Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.98,0:01:34.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以问一个问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.91,0:01:36.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,F3 皇后
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.48,0:01:37.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.53,0:01:39.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,G7 国王
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.90,0:01:42.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我出阵真的没问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.31,0:01:43.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,E4 塔楼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.52,0:01:45.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我死掉的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.77,0:01:47.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Deucalion的Aldnoah会停止的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.19,0:01:49.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这我懂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.67,0:01:51.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,D8 塔楼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.74,0:01:54.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 船到桥头自然直
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.47,0:01:58.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说界冢少尉想退出前线吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.45,0:01:59.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.57,0:02:01.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想出战
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.34,0:02:03.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,F6 皇后 将军
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.84,0:02:06.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿掉皇后 F6 国王
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.76,0:02:08.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我们的意见就一致了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.69,0:02:11.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,E5 主教 将军
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.89,0:02:13.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我将棋盘显示出来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.32,0:02:17.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚那招是你想的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.11,0:02:20.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是那个分析引擎所得出的结论呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.11,0:02:20.79,ruby,NTP,0,145,0,,analytical engine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.29,0:02:22.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,7比3的比例是我想出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.08,0:02:24.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,7比3？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.55,0:02:27.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我将任务分配给未使用的脑细胞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.28,0:02:29.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尝试优化处理效率
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.71,0:02:32.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此这既是机械装置提出的方案
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.86,0:02:34.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是我自己的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.76,0:02:37.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这艘船及船员们都欠你一条命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.43,0:02:40.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你想战斗的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.08,0:02:42.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们应该会支持你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.93,0:02:48.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是那么特别的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.08,0:02:52.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用后续提取的公主殿下的血液
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.50,0:02:55.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进行Aldnoah启动实验的事你听说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.01,0:02:58.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,G5 国王
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.00,0:03:00.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实验结果都失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.54,0:03:03.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,单依靠血液不足以满足启动条件
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.47,0:03:05.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少尉可以称作一个相当特殊的例子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.15,0:03:09.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在对公主殿下进行急救的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.93,0:03:15.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感染上的启动因子在接触皇族血液后活性化了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.07,0:03:17.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在过去10个多月的时间里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.97,0:03:22.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得到了很多关于Aldnoah和他们的重甲骑兵的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.56,0:03:27.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是敌我双方军事力的差距依然是压倒性的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.92,0:03:30.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按目前这个状况继续作战…不知道我们是否能赢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.14,0:03:35.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 界冢少尉 我想在你身上赌一把
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.76,0:03:39.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,G7 主教
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.41,0:03:43.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要认输吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.38,0:03:47.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚那手是你想出来的？还是你的左眼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.78,0:03:49.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任凭你的想像了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.95,0:04:02.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是Tharsis也没办法看到如此遥远的未来么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.49,0:04:19.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.24,0:04:19.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.12,0:04:32.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎您回来 斯雷因大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.42,0:04:35.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我将枪弹集中到了哈库莱特先生所计算的范围内
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.15,0:04:39.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后就祈祷那些子弹不会受到额外的风的影响吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.20,0:04:42.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 我还以为是什么味呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.12,0:04:45.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来有狗混了进来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.13,0:04:47.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还是个肮脏货
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.42,0:04:49.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来这里做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.54,0:04:55.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴鲁库如斯伯爵 马丽尔晌伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.54,0:04:55.61,ruby,NTP,0,350,0,,Barouhcruz
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.54,0:04:55.61,ruby,NTP,230,0,0,,Marylcian
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.14,0:04:58.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是奉命前来参战的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.75,0:05:00.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地球的狗…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.22,0:05:01.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真敢口出狂言
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.91,0:05:09.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扎赫巴姆伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.44,0:05:11.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这斯雷因·托罗亚特是我的家臣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.17,0:05:13.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若是他对你有所不敬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.26,0:05:14.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我代他向你谢罪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.16,0:05:17.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 如果你无端地侮辱他的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.16,0:05:19.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马丽尔晌伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.27,0:05:21.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是不会放过你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.59,0:05:24.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你养个地球人当宠物的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.24,0:05:25.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就当你一时兴起不说什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.76,0:05:27.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你将其提拔成骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.60,0:05:29.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这玩笑开得有点大了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.07,0:05:35.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴鲁库如斯伯爵 还轮不到你对我的家臣说三道四
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.66,0:05:39.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 如果要一起战斗的话 就另当别论了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.51,0:05:41.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和随时会背叛的人在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.72,0:05:43.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁能放心作战
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.66,0:05:46.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 就请您在这里将我杀了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.69,0:05:49.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正如您所言
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.60,0:05:51.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果就这样与两位一起披挂上阵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.55,0:05:54.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难保我不会背后遭人暗算
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.74,0:05:56.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这狗娘养的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.65,0:05:57.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诸位！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.83,0:05:58.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好听着 诸位！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.74,0:06:03.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在巴斯皇帝的恩典下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.27,0:06:05.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在此宣布
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.94,0:06:09.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我收斯雷因·托罗亚特为子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.33,0:06:13.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在场的各位是我的见证人！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.02,0:06:15.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伯爵…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.50,0:06:17.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站起来 斯雷因
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.26,0:06:20.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从今天开始 你就是我的儿子了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.11,0:06:26.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还要对他出手吗 马丽尔晌伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.56,0:06:31.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然贵公有如此觉悟的话 此事就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.22,0:06:34.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是他若有丝毫可疑之举
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.49,0:06:37.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会毫不留情把他处斩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.12,0:06:42.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.87,0:06:44.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我的缘故导致这样的事态
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.83,0:06:47.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无所谓 很久之前我就已经决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.72,0:06:50.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是出入战场的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.08,0:06:53.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以必须及早决定继承人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.63,0:06:56.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今后你就视我为父亲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.69,0:07:09.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜您 斯雷因大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.56,0:07:11.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成为了伯爵的继承人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.68,0:07:15.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来您离梦想就更近一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.76,0:07:17.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这样 哈库莱特先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.88,0:07:20.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我哪有什么梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.07,0:07:24.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即将开始了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.64,0:07:25.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.32,0:07:30.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认为哪边会赢呢 艾德尔丽泽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.31,0:07:36.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当…当然会是我巴斯帝国军获得胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.60,0:07:38.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？这样好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.33,0:07:42.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联合军中有你朋友所乘的飞船吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.53,0:07:44.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊！我没有地球的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.37,0:07:46.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.39,0:07:47.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我们打个赌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.74,0:07:48.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打赌？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.93,0:07:50.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来赌赌看巴斯帝国能否获得胜利…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.36,0:07:53.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就赌…我想想…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.78,0:07:55.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如皇姐大人的生命…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.43,0:07:58.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.96,0:08:06.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皇姐大人现在到底在做着什么样的梦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Part 2
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.78,0:08:15.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看到韵子了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.77,0:08:19.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该和莱埃一起在电磁弹射器那边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.44,0:08:20.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.99,0:08:22.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可别迷路了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.44,0:08:23.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.35,0:08:27.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,运动裤！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.53,0:08:29.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐太朗 你太贪心了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.62,0:08:34.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tharsis 详细能力不明
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.70,0:08:38.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有报告说其回避率很高
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.05,0:08:40.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前确认的驾驶员是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.12,0:08:45.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯雷因·托罗亚特
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.90,0:08:50.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我来地球前 一位与我很亲密的地球人送我的护身符
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.94,0:08:52.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在空中飞翔的生物…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.71,0:08:55.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟斯雷因说的一样…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.49,0:09:00.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道他也安装了与神经连接的分析引擎吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.85,0:09:05.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是这样就说得通了…不过 目前数据还是太少了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.55,0:09:08.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那回避方式就像是预测未来似的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.13,0:09:14.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果真是如此的话…就麻烦了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.79,0:09:15.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自言自语？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.01,0:09:19.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在和我自己对话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.44,0:09:20.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是自言自语吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.08,0:09:28.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驾驭着八足神兽斯雷普尼尔的军神奥丁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.08,0:09:33.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在喝下密米尔之泉的泉水后虽然获得了庞大的知识
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.59,0:09:38.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但代价是失去了自己的左眼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.98,0:09:39.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是北欧神话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.10,0:09:41.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你挺博识的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.41,0:09:43.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙一直当我是个笨蛋是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.57,0:09:48.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,俄罗斯那场战斗之后
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.14,0:09:50.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾想下船
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.96,0:09:53.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我当时吓坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.34,0:09:58.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那样的话到了那个世界叫我怎样面对起助…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.57,0:10:02.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你的坐骑状态不好的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.25,0:10:03.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随时都可以来找我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.69,0:10:05.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上给你修好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.69,0:10:06.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靠你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.27,0:10:09.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 在出击之前去吃点什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.33,0:10:11.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有点时间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.24,0:10:13.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.48,0:10:16.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说我被击中的时候 胃里是空的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.92,0:10:19.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此内脏没有被胃里的残留物所污染
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.87,0:10:21.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才捡回了一条命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.29,0:10:22.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.09,0:10:25.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是机会难得
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.71,0:10:27.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去喝杯茶还是可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.01,0:10:30.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,选什么卷盘呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.01,0:10:30.34,ruby,NTP,105,0,0,,reel
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.48,0:10:34.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1号到3号 再加上紧急用的10号
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.68,0:10:36.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,左右各放1个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.35,0:10:38.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是高重力回转配置呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.38,0:10:40.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用那些又长又细的线缆不合我性格
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.47,0:10:41.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.48,0:10:43.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 Deucalion小队
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.41,0:10:45.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传说中的Aldnoah部队吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.97,0:10:47.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说她是火星人来着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.78,0:10:51.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在战场上可别拖我们后腿哦 小姐们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.88,0:10:55.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些家伙搞啥啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.17,0:10:56.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人渣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.29,0:10:57.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是他们没有说错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.82,0:11:00.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火星人都是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.16,0:11:03.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这点我最懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.37,0:11:10.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很可爱呢 莱埃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.88,0:11:12.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就喜欢恶狠狠的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.35,0:11:13.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.16,0:11:14.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再多向我们撒撒娇也没问题哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.21,0:11:16.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说啥啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.26,0:11:17.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要吃糖吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.43,0:11:18.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打飞你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.39,0:11:21.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们将在30分后进入防空领域
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.14,0:11:23.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请出击
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.32,0:11:24.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝你们武运昌隆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.32,0:11:30.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的爱机呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.46,0:11:32.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经全部调整完毕了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.62,0:11:33.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.40,0:11:37.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Dioscuria II 出击！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.61,0:11:45.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯雷因·托罗亚特 Tharsis 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.71,0:11:49.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Stygis队 出击！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.90,0:12:03.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火星重甲骑兵队接近！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.88,0:12:05.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通告全部队
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.31,0:12:06.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作战开始！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.86,0:12:08.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,司令总部来电
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.48,0:12:09.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是作战开始的命令！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.10,0:12:11.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Deucalion发射！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.12,0:12:15.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本舰作为游击队去增援攻击队
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.85,0:12:17.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全舰战斗态势
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.64,0:12:21.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本舰的舰载机从三叉戟基地出击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.26,0:12:25.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mustang-11 允许发射
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.26,0:12:25.94,ruby,NTP,245,0,0,,cleared for launch
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.05,0:12:29.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解 Mustang-11 允许发射
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.85,0:12:30.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发射
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.85,0:12:30.71,ruby,NTP,0,0,0,,Blast off
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.85,0:12:38.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发射
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.74,0:12:56.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与目标交会 开始攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.74,0:12:56.32,ruby,NTP,0,185,0,,Target merge
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.39,0:13:05.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌方开始攻击了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.54,0:13:08.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不到时候…反正在这种强风中也不会命中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.05,0:13:10.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等对方再靠近些再射击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.93,0:13:12.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等对方再靠近些再射击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.04,0:13:14.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等对方再靠近些再射击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.26,0:13:17.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,防护伞被干掉了!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.91,0:13:19.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mustang-11
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.04,0:13:20.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.31,0:13:24.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过因为碎片引起的震动让我无法瞄准
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.84,0:13:27.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mustang-00 进行援护
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.64,0:13:34.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊奈帆！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.25,0:13:39.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 你的伞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.76,0:13:41.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这只是蒙蒙细雨 没有必要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.05,0:13:43.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你别乱来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.71,0:13:45.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正近战的时候也用不上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.29,0:13:49.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,推测重力变化 数据补正结束
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.44,0:13:51.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发射！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.09,0:13:53.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始攻击！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.49,0:13:57.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.08,0:14:06.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使用电缆绕星变轨回转
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.00,0:14:08.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回归战斗区域
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.88,0:14:09.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3号 发射！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.56,0:14:23.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离回转结束还剩 4秒 3 2 1…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.20,0:14:24.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解除
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.83,0:14:38.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,界冢伊奈帆！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.42,0:14:41.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯雷因·托罗亚特…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.38,0:14:48.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有30秒将到达马里内罗基地的最近点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.62,0:14:50.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主炮发射准备结束
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.13,0:14:51.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通告全部队
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.49,0:14:53.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他们撤出射线轴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.96,0:14:54.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莱埃！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.80,0:14:57.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是Rhinelander-22!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.60,0:14:59.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 我被抄后了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.47,0:15:03.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解 Mustang-22 前来援护
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.49,0:15:10.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火星人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.84,0:15:13.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马里内罗基地进入射程了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.74,0:15:15.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射线轴上没有友军机
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.53,0:15:16.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主炮发射！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.33,0:15:25.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马里内罗基地开始拉开距离
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.92,0:15:28.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向攻击队和游击队下达撤退命令
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.09,0:15:30.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他们转入防守
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.36,0:15:32.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊奈帆 下达撤退命令了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.26,0:15:32.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快回来！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.27,0:15:35.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊奈帆！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.60,0:15:43.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,精准的射击呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.27,0:15:49.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然…那家伙也在预测
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.52,0:15:51.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1号回转
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.05,0:16:02.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在他出从岩石那边出现的一瞬间射击
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.09,0:16:06.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他会在我从岩石那边出现的一瞬间攻过来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.50,0:16:08.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐标确认
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.81,0:16:10.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离着弹还有2分
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.52,0:16:12.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.64,0:16:14.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发射！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.39,0:16:25.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打中了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.29,0:16:28.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.98,0:16:30.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧 斯雷因
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.28,0:16:31.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,退下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.39,0:16:33.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我还能战
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.39,0:16:34.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别勉强
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.84,0:16:35.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,橙色的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.42,0:16:38.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有账要和他算
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.96,0:16:49.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,防护壁的缝隙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.08,0:16:52.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经改变了它的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.39,0:16:58.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞吧 我的眷属们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.71,0:17:23.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连接到能源结合处
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.83,0:17:25.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剑刃力场展开
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.93,0:17:30.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拔刀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.82,0:17:40.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别想跑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.58,0:17:44.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊奈帆 我来掩护你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.54,0:17:45.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快跑 伊奈帆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.66,0:17:46.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你别过来 韵子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.03,0:17:47.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.77,0:17:48.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.69,0:17:49.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.55,0:17:50.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你待在那个位置就好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.85,0:17:53.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉悟吧 地球人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.28,0:17:56.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,右方反冲推进器 抛弃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.28,0:17:56.36,ruby,NTP,0,0,0,,kick thruster
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.68,0:17:57.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发射！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.84,0:18:06.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火焰没有被吸入
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.42,0:18:07.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里就是防护壁的缝隙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.75,0:18:18.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别想跑！斯雷因！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.71,0:18:28.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.69,0:18:30.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高速碎片的集群
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.95,0:18:35.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3次元多普勒雷达检测到了急速接近的云层反应
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.36,0:18:37.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 韵子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.96,0:18:39.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果晚一步的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.77,0:18:42.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也会被卷入其中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.90,0:18:49.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能！区区的碎片怎能伤到这架Dioscuria
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.11,0:18:51.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并不是碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.12,0:18:53.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是枪弹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.85,0:18:55.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在开战之前进行了射击
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.75,0:18:58.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让子弹绕着地球卫星轨道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.82,0:19:02.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正好于此刻在这一带着弹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.42,0:19:04.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯雷因？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.12,0:19:08.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来这是用来打倒界冢伊奈帆而设的陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.27,0:19:11.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然这个策略的难关在于需要将次元防护壁无效化
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.32,0:19:14.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我相信他办得到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.62,0:19:15.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯雷因…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.39,0:19:16.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.93,0:19:23.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的相信我会效忠于你吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.16,0:19:31.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得我会原谅向亚瑟拉姆公主殿下开枪的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.96,0:19:37.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第2波差不多该到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.31,0:19:40.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.83,0:19:45.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.12,0:19:52.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也挺好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.97,0:20:15.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在这一天 失去了第2位父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.59,0:20:22.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是一同为巴斯帝国的繁荣而鞠躬尽瘁的伟大人物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.31,0:20:26.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在此宣布将继承父亲们的遗志
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.46,0:20:32.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为巴斯帝国更加繁荣昌盛而战斗到底
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.68,0:20:34.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位巴斯骑士的侯爵们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.09,0:20:37.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不是我们窝里斗的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.94,0:20:40.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为崇高的巴斯帝国的骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.64,0:20:41.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道我们不应该精诚合作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.03,0:20:45.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将地球的反抗势力一扫而光吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.82,0:20:48.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}以亚瑟拉姆·巴斯·艾莉欧西亚殿下之名
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.32,0:20:52.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}制裁那些违抗巴斯帝国的地球人们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.58,0:20:57.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}亚瑟拉姆公主殿下在月球基地等待着那一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.12,0:20:52.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙没有说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.56,0:20:59.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然…她还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.88,0:21:07.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大人 您辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.46,0:21:14.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈库莱特先生是第三阶级出身的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.15,0:21:15.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.17,0:21:18.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我的家境贫寒 身份低微
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.06,0:21:21.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我的父母依然含辛茹苦将我抚养成人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.74,0:21:25.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用尽各种手段把我送到了轨道骑士麾下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.81,0:21:28.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 斯雷因大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.88,0:21:32.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身为地球人却成功赢得了爵位的您
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.40,0:21:36.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打心底佩服
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.36,0:21:48.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来就是我们的时代了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.60,0:21:52.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走吧 哈库莱特
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.28,0:21:55.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.92,0:22:00.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯雷因·扎赫巴姆·托罗亚特伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.89,0:22:10.89,title,NTP,0,0,0,,“旋转的陷阱”
